OL,3,CSmell from wheelie bin was woman's body
OL,5,FA man who stuffed a woman's body in a
OL,6,Fbin before disposing of it when
OL,7,Fneighbours complained about the smell
OL,8,Fhas been convicted of killing her.
OL,10,FMark Metcalfe, 40, dumped 32-year-old
OL,11,FTerri Jordan's body in undergrowth
OL,12,Fnear an Asda store in Harehills,
OL,13,FLeeds, where it was found on 23 June
OL,14,F2022.
OL,16,FLeeds Crown Court heard she probably
OL,17,Fdied around 12 days earlier. Her
OL,18,Fremains were so badly decomposed it
OL,19,Fwas impossible to determine how she
OL,20,Fdied.
