OL,5,FHe then tried to cover his tracks by
OL,6,Fabandoning the wheelie bin elsewhere
OL,7,Fand disposing of Ms Jordan's clothing
OL,8,Fand other incriminating items in other
OL,9,Fbins.
OL,11,FTraces of Ms Jordan's blood and hair
OL,12,Fwere found in Metcalfe's living room.
OL,14,FA jury cleared Metcalfe of murder but
OL,15,Fconvicted him of manslaughter.
OL,17,FSam Jackson, of the Crown Prosecution
OL,18,FService, said: "Mark Metcalfe is a
OL,19,Fbrutal killer. He ended Terri Jordan's
OL,20,Flife and disposed of her remains in
OL,21,Fthe most callous way possible.
